/**
 * Station 3 - Remembering Things with Variables
 *
 * ============================================================
 * LEARNING INTENT:
 * ============================================================
 * - Primary concept: Variables store values so you don't have to repeat yourself
 * - Supporting concepts: const vs let, naming conventions, assignment operator
 * - Explicit non-goals: Functions, scope, hoisting
